==English==

===Etymology===
From the name of a fictional town called [[w:Lilliput and Blefuscu|Lilliput]] in the novel ''[[w:Gulliver's Travels|Gulliver's Travels]]'' by [[w:Jonathan Swift|Jonathan Swift]]
===Noun===
'''lilliputian'''
# A very small person or being

===Adjective===
# Very small, diminutive
# Trivial, petty

[[vi:lilliputian]]